          <td height="45" VALIGN="TOP" bgcolor="#333333"><div class="topictitle"><table border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0 width=100%>
      <tr>
       <td>
	   <div align="left" class="storytitle">A Rogue by Any Other Name: An Interview with Vanguard's Darrin McPherson</div>
	   <div align="left" class="storyauth">By Fricka</div>
	   <div align="left" class="storydetail">Aug 12, 2005, 12:37</div>
    
       </td>
       <td align=right valign=top>
      <div align="right" class="newslink"><a class="newslink" href="mailto:?subject=A%20Rogue%20by%20Any%20Other%20Name%3A%20An%20Interview%20with%20Vanguard%27s%20Darrin%20McPherson&body=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesafehouse.org%2Farticles%2Finterviews%2Farticle_6.php">Email&nbsp;this&nbsp;article</a></div>
      <div align="right" class="newslink"><a class="newslink" href="http://www.thesafehouse.org/articles/interviews/printer_6.php">Printer&nbsp;friendly&nbsp;page</a></div>
	  <div align="right" class="newslink"><a class="newslink" href="/cgi-bin/articles/exec/goforum.cgi?id=6&cat=27">Discuss this story</a></div>
	  </td>
      </tr>
     </table></div>
  
  
  </td>
</tr>
