o I gave him the rapid fire drill. <br><br><span style="FONT-WEIGHT:bold">Pancakes or waffles?</span> - Pancakes <br><span style="FONT-WEIGHT:bold">Muffins or pie?</span> - Pie, sour cream and lemon <br><span style="FONT-WEIGHT:bold">Vanilla or chocolate?</span> - Chocolate <br><br>Well Darrin may not like the word “rogue” but I think it might be the waffle, muffin and vanilla folks who might be the one’s he’ll have to watch out for. As for me, I’ll give him a little bit of a break to work on the game -- at least until next I see him. Then we’ll have to have another update on the rogue/thief/ninja class. Whatever name it will go by, I’m sure it will be as sweet.</div>
